this.width=200" /><br />Follow the fortunes of your favourite national team by adding this Widget, which charts whether they&#039;ve move up or down the monthly FIFA/Coca-Cola World Ranking. <br /><br /><strong>World Leagues Block:</strong><br /><img src=\'http://www.fifa.com/img/widgets/worldmatchcentre/worldleagues.png\' border=\'0\' alt=\'\' onload="JavaScript:if(this.width>200) this.width=200" /><br />Get up to the minute results and standings from your favourite leagues, as well as the latest news. A scrolling ticker also gives up-to-the minute scores. <br /><br /><strong>Download:</strong> <a href="http://www.arabxoops.com/modules/mydownloads/singlefile.php?cid=3&lid=437" rel="external" title="">click here</a> <br /><br />Enjoy <img class="imgsmile" src="http://www.xoops.org/uploads/smil48a81b5cc3491.gif" alt="" /><br /><br /><br /><br />',
    'pubdate' => 'Sat, 12 Jun 2010 21:02:54 -0000',
    'guid' => 'http://www.xoops.org/modules/news/article.php?storyid=5439',
